@startuml hibernation-wake
title DeckMux — CF Worker Hibernation Recovery

skinparam backgroundColor #0d1117
skinparam defaultFontColor #c9d1d9
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #58a6ff
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #30363d
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #30363d
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #161b22
skinparam noteBorderColor #30363d
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #161b22

participant "Browser A" as A
participant "CF Worker\n(Durable Object)" as DO
participant "Browser B" as B

note over DO: Hibernated\n(>30s no messages)\nPresence state lost

A -> A: user scrolls
A -> DO: presence_update {scroll_line: 42}
note over DO: **Wake from hibernation**\nPresenceStore is empty

DO -> B: presence_update {user_id: A, ...}
note over B: Received message after gap\nLast sent presence >10s ago\nTriggering re-announce

B -> DO: presence_update {scroll_line: 15, ...}
DO -> A: presence_update {user_id: B, ...}
note over A,B: Both have fresh presence\nRecovery < 200ms

@enduml
